{"tid":439097,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"(大學生入）有冇人識做呢條題目？","createTime":"2017-10-17T13:37:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T12:30:34.000Z","uid":140522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"9a697794b5de875099528304d129cf6ab7d1880e","tid":439097,"uid":140522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:37:52.000Z","msg":"Starting from its depot in town X, a delivery lorry is to make deliveries to three towns A, B and C, in any order which the driver chooses and finally to return to X.<br />\n<br />\nStraight roads connect each town to every other town.<br />\n<br />\nDepending on the layout of the towns, which of the following could NOT be the shortest journey for him to take?<br />\n<br />\nA . XAXBCBX<br />\n<br />\nB. XACBX<br />\n<br />\nC. XAXBCX<br />\n<br />\nD. XBABXCX<br />\n<br />\nE. XABCBAX<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：純邏輯題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69aa2193579bfa5657e5ac6ae4407aa5c2a729c7","tid":439097,"uid":140522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:38:38.000Z","msg":"答案係c"},{"pid":"10112a05d89d05cc6105abf2202078a926f8b99a","tid":439097,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:40:34.000Z","msg":"C"},{"pid":"1b07b6981e2adee38feba278608d0698678c150e","tid":439097,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:46:13.000Z","msg":"答案係B呀 個答案係B呀"},{"pid":"8dfdc1bb58dc41fca619c75bdd51d57503d4bb03","tid":439097,"uid":140522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"真係唔識做，求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebea6449019b72703d679373ba7fe370dc453964","tid":439097,"uid":22906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T13:58:04.000Z","msg":"呢題個地圖係咪好似一個等邊三角形咁，三隻角係ABC，而中間就係X<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc25e843f506a1430508ae417dd7720a90f59ea","tid":439097,"uid":5172,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:03:23.000Z","msg":"李克用"},{"pid":"ed6704e5ffcd3f906b83ebfddca1de344db22829","tid":439097,"uid":102978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:05:47.000Z","msg":"男人婆！叫晒啲膊頭有花既入黎"},{"pid":"8645eceb9b9f9483ba4beeea33f2625b6a2592d6","tid":439097,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"Triangle inequality?"},{"pid":"a25763032b2f63b2ad500c7bee265a66fffab35e","tid":439097,"uid":838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:13:03.000Z","msg":"XAXBCX<br />\n<br />\nAX + XB &gt; AB<br />\n<br />\n所以呢條唔可能最短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d2245d631cce14961041b8dfc36e687a107e2f","tid":439097,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:16:59.000Z","msg":"B"},{"pid":"6843edd8afb82b7c74930c29884afef783db5bd9","tid":439097,"uid":74019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:21:37.000Z","msg":"A . XAXBCBX<br />\nC.  XAXBCX<br />\n<br />\nA最後要行CBX, C只需行CX<br />\n因為係直路, 所以CB+BX&gt;=CX<br />\n<br />\n因此A唔可能最短"},{"pid":"60d45cac15ff13e02d7d72d0eb2fedf204d2c38d","tid":439097,"uid":71584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:24:26.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"7922f934a2c40afd1d0dc1898f75ba2832ca575e","tid":439097,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:27:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>XAXBCX<br />\n<br />\nAX + XB &gt; AB<br />\n<br />\n所以呢條唔可能最短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n補充多啲<br />\n<br />\n如果XAXBCX係最短<br />\n咁一定要做到AX+XB &lt;= AB<br />\n亦即係AXB共線<br />\n<br />\n若AXB共線：<br />\nBCX亦代表CX &lt; CB + BX<br />\n即係代表BCX三點非共線<br />\n<br />\n若BCX三點非共線<br />\n咁一開始喺A應該去咗C先再去B先會最短<br />\n<br />\n亦即XAXBCX不可能最短"},{"pid":"7f0b29855cbdbb3338e4e2e0d23030a3fd648e5b","tid":439097,"uid":137740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>A . XAXBCBX<br />\nC.  XAXBCX<br />\n<br />\nA最後要行CBX, C只需行CX<br />\n因為係直路, 所以CB+BX&gt;=CX<br />\n<br />\n因此A唔可能最短</blockquote><br />\n如果條路係 A-X-B-C 呢個結構<br />\n咁XAXBCBX就係最短路程"},{"pid":"da149f44ff7c270b343bc2cbb26ceaac0eee3c60","tid":439097,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:31:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>A . XAXBCBX<br />\nC.  XAXBCX<br />\n<br />\nA最後要行CBX, C只需行CX<br />\n因為係直路, 所以CB+BX&gt;=CX<br />\n<br />\n因此A唔可能最短</blockquote><br />\n如果條路係 A-X-B-C 呢個結構<br />\n咁XAXBC<span style=\"color: red;\">B</span>X就係最短路程</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n題目就係爭咗個B字"},{"pid":"5435cbdbee0f2523f406d4fbf5dbe3876de81604","tid":439097,"uid":31237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:38:05.000Z","msg":"用vector試緊"},{"pid":"036fa0aa0c3050eb23b50da8be61ef7c4216edf6","tid":439097,"uid":141113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>A . XAXBCBX<br />\nC.  XAXBCX<br />\n<br />\nA最後要行CBX, C只需行CX<br />\n因為係直路, 所以CB+BX&gt;=CX<br />\n<br />\n因此A唔可能最短</blockquote><br />\n如果條路係 A-X-B-C 呢個結構<br />\n咁XAXBC<span style=\"color: red;\">B</span>X就係最短路程</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n題目就係爭咗個B字</blockquote><br />\n西利"},{"pid":"0bf3b35712207a219ae63bf7274719f34b8cfa69","tid":439097,"uid":137740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:42:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>A . XAXBCBX<br />\nC.  XAXBCX<br />\n<br />\nA最後要行CBX, C只需行CX<br />\n因為係直路, 所以CB+BX&gt;=CX<br />\n<br />\n因此A唔可能最短</blockquote><br />\n如果條路係 A-X-B-C 呢個結構<br />\n咁XAXBC<span style=\"color: red;\">B</span>X就係最短路程</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n題目就係爭咗個B字</blockquote><br />\nA. 咪就係有個B字囉<br />\n當CX=CBX嘅時候，XAXBCX 的確係最短<br />\n(但係回程你一定會穿過B，所以要寫埋出嚟，呢個情況C唔成立)<br />\n<br />\n如果地圖上面個C搬上/落少少就可以用XAXBCX啦<br />\n但係呢個時候optimal solution就會係XACBX<br />\n所以C再次唔成立"},{"pid":"8680cb831dd3b0a666cdd95e4ad0f92d5756b181","tid":439097,"uid":2843,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:42:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/224248_b256690e81066de06bd594e2a191fe46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F224248_b256690e81066de06bd594e2a191fe46.jpg&h=1a08c874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nC <br />\n如圖"},{"pid":"08768ba0e47b1e41fc39d39cbcbf1b8889f4c921","tid":439097,"uid":137740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:45:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/224248_b256690e81066de06bd594e2a191fe46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F224248_b256690e81066de06bd594e2a191fe46.jpg&h=1a08c874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nC <br />\n如圖</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1c91ca1d2aac9de18da5c97e3440d2524e7ee46","tid":439097,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T14:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/224248_b256690e81066de06bd594e2a191fe46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F224248_b256690e81066de06bd594e2a191fe46.jpg&h=1a08c874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nC <br />\n如圖</blockquote><br />\n圖畫係一個好嘅表達辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但只能講到ABDE唔係答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要再解C係答案就要詳細好多"},{"pid":"915d86740e996544f08e5b1f2119e64ae8a34dc5","tid":439097,"uid":74019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>A . XAXBCBX<br />\nC.  XAXBCX<br />\n<br />\nA最後要行CBX, C只需行CX<br />\n因為係直路, 所以CB+BX&gt;=CX<br />\n<br />\n因此A唔可能最短</blockquote><br />\n如果條路係 A-X-B-C 呢個結構<br />\n咁XAXBC<span style=\"color: red;\">B</span>X就係最短路程</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n題目就係爭咗個B字</blockquote><br />\nA. 咪就係有個B字囉<br />\n當CX=CBX嘅時候，XAXBCX 的確係最短<br />\n(但係回程你一定會穿過B，所以要寫埋出嚟，呢個情況C唔成立)<br />\n<br />\n如果地圖上面個C搬上/落少少就可以用XAXBCX啦<br />\n但係呢個時候optimal solution就會係XACBX<br />\n所以C再次唔成立</blockquote><br />\n冇認真睇,解錯左做好似搭地鐵咁C站上X站落, 就算經過B都唔洗寫出黎<br />\n但睇返XAXB就知唔係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9de354dae0c413166bde53d2a864c5a5fdeb24d6","tid":439097,"uid":54076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T15:05:47.000Z","msg":"唔講長定短<br />\nC根本唔可能<br />\n（好似係）"},{"pid":"111a4d3d46cf99e59d8fc8f4f6ffed4e872996da","tid":439097,"uid":2843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-18T04:38:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/17/224248_b256690e81066de06bd594e2a191fe46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F17%2F224248_b256690e81066de06bd594e2a191fe46.jpg&h=1a08c874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nC <br />\n如圖</blockquote><br />\n圖畫係一個好嘅表達辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但只能講到ABDE唔係答案<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要再解C係答案就要詳細好多</blockquote><br />\n咪解左囉，因為AC 短d"}]}